title: Nike Teams up with Demi Vollering and FDJ-Suez for Its First Pro Cycling Team Partnership
content:
Sporting super-brand Nike joins Women's WorldTour squad in unique partnership: 'It will strengthen our identity and bring a fresh dimension.'

Read the full article at Nike Teams up with Demi Vollering and FDJ-Suez for Its First Pro Cycling Team Partnership on Velo.
author: Jim Cotton
